A giant cloud of steam formed over the ocean just west of the Azores Islands 
as millions of gallons of water were evaporated, but that's what happens 
when a giant flaming intergalactic cruiser crashes into the ocean.  Despite 
his lethargy Razorclaw stood up and looked at the rest of his team. Seeing 
that they are all right he gives a half smile before barking out some 
orders.

*Razorclaw*  "Alright predacons, we made it back, but we need some way to 
get out of here..."

  After a few minutes of searching they found what they were looking for: 
the docking tube. Grabbing the remote for use of the tube Razorclaw led the 
rest of the predacons out into the world.
